  "critical": false,
  "description": "Nanometer-precision positioning, wafer stages, vibration isolation, and encoder feedback systems for semiconductor lithography and metrology equipment. Distinct from machine tools (which shape material) — precision motion controls position with nanometer accuracy using piezo actuators, air bearings, linear motors, laser interferometers, and active vibration cancellation. Organized by precision ladder: from micrometer linear stages to sub-5 nm wafer scanner positioning.",
